---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import stats from '../data/stats.json';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const readPct = Math.round(100 * stats.reading_progress.read / stats.total_books);
const wantPct = 100 - readPct;
const yearsToFinish = Math.round(stats.bookshelf.estimated_reading_hours / 8 / 365 * 10) / 10;
---

<Layout title="About" description="What is tsundoku? The Japanese art of acquiring books and letting them pile up.">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">About</h1>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-purple-400 mb-3">積ん読 — Tsundoku</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        <strong class="text-white">Tsundoku</strong> (積ん読) is a beautiful Japanese word for the act of acquiring books and letting them pile up without reading them. It combines <em>tsunde-oku</em> (to pile things up) with <em>doku</em> (to read).
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        It's not hoarding. It's <em>aspirational collecting</em>. Every unread book is a promise to your future self — a future self who apparently has unlimited free time and zero interest in sleep.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        This site is a monument to that optimism: {stats.total_books.toLocaleString()} books cataloged, {readPct}% read, and roughly {yearsToFinish} years of nonstop reading to finish the rest. But who's counting?
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-purple-400 mb-3">The Numbers</h2>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 p-6">
        <dl class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-sm">
          <div>
            <dt class="text-gray-500">Books cataloged</dt>
            <dd class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">{stats.total_books.toLocaleString()}</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="text-gray-500">Actually read</dt>
            <dd class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-400">{readPct}%</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="text-gray-500">Still "planning to"</dt>
            <dd class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-400">{wantPct}%</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="text-gray-500">Total pages</dt>
            <dd class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">{stats.bookshelf.total_pages.toLocaleString()}</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="text-gray-500">Shelf space needed</dt>
            <dd class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">{stats.bookshelf.shelf_meters}m</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="text-gray-500">Hours to read all</dt>
            <dd class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">{stats.bookshelf.estimated_reading_hours.toLocaleString()}</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-purple-400 mb-3">Free Reading</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Many books in this collection are in the public domain. We've linked to free reading and listening sources wherever available:
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">
        <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-green-400 font-bold">1,003</span> books linked to
          <a href="https://www.gutenberg.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300 transition-colors">Project Gutenberg</a>
          for free reading
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-amber-400 font-bold">717</span> books linked to
          <a href="https://librivox.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300 transition-colors">LibriVox</a>
          for free audiobooks
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-blue-400 font-bold">134</span> books linked to
          <a href="https://www.hathitrust.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300 transition-colors">HathiTrust Digital Library</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-purple-400 mb-3">How It's Built</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        This is a fully static site — no server, no database, no JavaScript frameworks fighting for your CPU. Just HTML, CSS, and a few Svelte islands for search and filtering.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-sm">
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 px-3 py-2">
          <span class="text-white font-medium">Astro</span>
          <span class="text-gray-500 block text-xs">Static site generator</span>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 px-3 py-2">
          <span class="text-white font-medium">Svelte 5</span>
          <span class="text-gray-500 block text-xs">Interactive islands</span>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 px-3 py-2">
          <span class="text-white font-medium">Tailwind CSS</span>
          <span class="text-gray-500 block text-xs">Styling</span>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 px-3 py-2">
          <span class="text-white font-medium">Open Library</span>
          <span class="text-gray-500 block text-xs">Covers & metadata</span>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 px-3 py-2">
          <span class="text-white font-medium">Wikipedia</span>
          <span class="text-gray-500 block text-xs">Descriptions & bios</span>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 px-3 py-2">
          <span class="text-white font-medium">GitHub Pages</span>
          <span class="text-gray-500 block text-xs">Hosting</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-purple-400 mb-3">Stages of Tsundoku</h2>
      <ol class="space-y-3 text-gray-300 text-sm list-decimal list-inside">
        <li><strong class="text-white">Denial</strong> — "I don't have a problem. I just appreciate good literature."</li>
        <li><strong class="text-white">Bargaining</strong> — "If I read two books a week, I'll finish by... 2029."</li>
        <li><strong class="text-white">Cataloging</strong> — "I should organize these into a database. With enrichment pipelines."</li>
        <li><strong class="text-white">Acceptance</strong> — "I built a website for my unread books. This is who I am now."</li>
        <li><strong class="text-white">Relapse</strong> — "Oh, that looks interesting..." <em>*adds 50 more books*</em></li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <div class="text-center pt-6 border-t border-gray-800">
      <a href={`${base}`} class="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300 transition-colors text-sm">
        ← Back to the pile
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
